<div class="patternContent"><div class="foswikiTopic"> <h1 id="System.PatternSkin_CSS_Cookbook">  <a href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkin">PatternSkin</a> CSS Cookbook </h1>
<p></p>

<strong>Questions and answers on how to customize the default look of Foswiki for your own needs, using style sheets.</strong> For configuring page elements, see <a href="/bin/view/System/PatternSkinCustomization">PatternSkinCustomization</a>.
<p></p>

<div class="foswikiToc" id="foswikiTOC"><span class="foswikiTocTitle">On this page:</span> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#First_Read:_How_to_modify_PatternSkin_styles"> First Read: How to modify PatternSkin styles </a> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#When_you_need_lots_of_graphic_changes:_Rewriting_CSS"> When you need lots of graphic changes: Rewriting CSS </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#When_you_need_to_make_small_adjustments:_Adding_to_existing_CSS"> When you need to make small adjustments: Adding to existing CSS </a>
</li></ul> 
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Recipes"> Recipes </a> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Hide_the_left_bar"> Hide the left bar </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Toggle_the_left_bar_on_small_screen"> Toggle the left bar on small screen </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Use_different_fonts"> Use different fonts </a>
